[src:do-178c/do-178c] "Guidance" conveys a slightly stronger sense of obligation than "guidelines".
[src:do-178c/do-178c] The entire DO-248C/ED-94C document, *Supporting Information for DO-178C and DO-278A*, falls into the "supporting information" category, not guidance.
